'''Shadow Killer''' was the name given to the most deadly and feared of the [[Dashade/Legends|Dashade]] hunters. [[Ket Maliss]], [[Veshikk Urk]], [[Akriss Veng]], and [[Khem Val]] were all Shadow Killers.

